            "supported_languages": "English<strong>*</strong>, German, Russian, French, Spanish - Spain, Japanese, Korean, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support",
            "reviews": "“The Adventures of Bertram Fiddle: Episode 2 might just have the most amount of puns in a videogame EVER”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://wolfsgamingblog.com/2017/08/24/the-adventures-of-bertram-fiddle-chapter-2-review-is-it-punny/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Wolf's Gaming Blog</a><br><br>“Der britische Humor zieht sich wie ein roter Faden durch das gesamte Adventure, was durch die individuelle Synchronisation hervorragend zur Geltung kommt.”<br>80% – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.adventure-treff.de/test/15017-bertram-fiddle-auf-moerderjagd-in-london\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Adventure Treff</a><br><br>“A Bleaker Predicklement is something special”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://indiegames.com/2017/08/the_worlds_punniest_detective_.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >http://indiegames.com/2017/08/the_worlds_punniest_detective_.html</a><br>",
